          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "# Welcome\n\nThis sample dashboard provides monitoring of CICS subsystems.  \nPlease use the filters at the top to select:  \n- The Prometheus Data Source that contains the z/OS metrics  \n- The SYSPLEX that you are interested in  \n- The SYSTEM running on the previously selected SYSPLEX  \n- The Service (CICS region) running on the previously selected SYSTEM  \n\nThe values presented are auto-populated based on what is available to query",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.4.6",
      "type": "text"
    },
